name: terrorism-south-asia
description: This project analyzes terrorism in South Asia using data from the Global Terrorism Database (GTD) and the South Asia Terrorism Database. It identifies patterns, trends, and clusters in terrorist activities through data-driven techniques like clustering and geospatial analysis. The insights gained are intended to support counter-terrorism efforts.

name: GraphCompression
description: GraphCompression is a Python script for simplifying protein interaction networks. It retrieves interaction data from the STRING API using protein information or a user-provided dataset, constructs an interaction graph, and applies Spectral Clustering. The output is a condensed network saved as a graph image and CSV file.
